Class Summary
PermissionInfo This class simply encapsulates the data that needs to be fetched from the server for the permissioning tool.
PermissionListing Tab item to display the permission info, roles list and mailing lists corresponding to a specified user and request.
PTCache Caches the display groups and fields for providing the request layout in the permission tool.

RequestFormDataPT Implementation of IRequestFormData for the permissioning tool.
RequestUpdatePT Extension of AbstractUpdateRequestForm to display the update form in the permissioning tool view.
RequestViewPT Extension of AbstractViewRequestForm to display the add form in the permissioning tool view.
UserFormView Tab Item to display the various request forms a specified user and request.
